nodes.text: The Skaak Tipper Compound was an underground facility located a short distance north of the city of Theed in the Western Great Grass Plains on the Mid Rim world of Naboo.
During the time of the Galactic Civil War, sometime following the Battle of Yavin in 0 BBY, the criminal organization known as the Skaak Tippers used the compound as a base.

Circa 1 ABY, Sergeant Bragg and the RSF Intelligence Division investigated the Skaak Tipper Compound while searching for the responsibles of a terrorist attack in Theed. In the meantime, the compound was attacked by Darkwalker spacers led by Jorgellansel. Later, the wanted murderer Hunnos Jarkey briefly took refuge in the Skaak Tipper Compound after he escaped the Royal Naboo Security Forces.
The Skaak Tipper Compound was a location in the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, prior to the game's closure on December 15, 2011.
